            . I lost my handkerchief last Wednesday se'ennight, about eight o'clock, walking down <placeName id="t17730626-59-crimeloc339">Houndsditch</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17730626-59-crimeloc339" type="placeName" value="Houndsditch"></interp>
